        options: ["Start oral ferrous sulfate and schedule follow-up in 3 months","Refer for upper endoscopy and colonoscopy to evaluate for GI source of blood loss, then start iron replacement","Order hemoglobin electrophoresis to rule out thalassemia","Transfuse 2 units of packed RBCs for symptomatic anemia"],
