        options: ["Drink a cup of black tea with the meal to enhance flavor and absorption","Pair the lentils with a source of vitamin C, such as bell peppers or tomatoes, and avoid tea or coffee with the meal","Take a calcium supplement with the meal to support bone health simultaneously","Add a glass of milk to the meal for additional protein and iron"],
